"{\"uid\": \"dailystar.co.uk-real-life-im-olympic-medalist-cant-buy-33444742\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympic heavyweight hero Emily Campbell has slammed gym brands for their lack of size-inclusive gear, revealing she struggles to find kit in her size in shops.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Campbell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emily Campbell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since snatching a silver at the Tokyo Olympics three years back in the +87kg category, the 30-year-old icon has pumped up her status as a plus-size trailblazer.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fast forward toParis Olympics 2024and Campbell grabbed Team GB's closing piece of shiny hardware with a bronze in the women's +81kg weightlifting class.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.7490778514452935e-12, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}, {\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 3.5425173641442927e-12, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hitting the platform with a hefty total of 288kg made up of 126kg in the snatch and a whopping 162kg clean and jerk, the British powerhouse rounded off her performance with a spectacular cartwheel on the stage.\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 604, 