ities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Where's my gym kit?\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of a sudden I am having to wear men's horrible baggy T-shirts that do not fit me or whatever.\\\"\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The influencer left internet users buzzing with her epic clap-back at the fashion industry, saying she's baffled by how bigger women are expected to hit the gym without having the right gear.\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fitness is for everyone, and everyone looks different.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We talk about how important that is so let us be inclusive with everyone,\\\" she told her followers.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Want all the biggest Lifestyle news straight to your inbox?Sign up for our free Daily Star Hot Topics newsletter.\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 2055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added that a brand wanted her to promote them but they did not go up to her size and any clothes she would wear would have to be specially made.\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But she said she did not want sponsorship from them, she just wanted them to \\\"do the right thing\\\" and \\\"make bigger clothes for girls to be able to fit into.\\\"\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TikTokusers praised her for being a role model for plus-size women.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One user said: \\\"Yes, this is true!\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Companies need to sort this out, there a need for sportswear in larger sizes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another wrote: \\\"What an articulate lady.\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Role model right there,\\\" while someone else penned: \\\"This!\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I started lifting because I watched Emily at the 2020 Olympics and finally saw a body like mine and was in awe.\\\"\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Listen to the full episode of theGreat Company podcast on Spotify here.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2820, \"end\": 2827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spotify\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Spotify\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spotify\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spotify\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New episodes are released every Tuesday.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"AtReach and across our entitieswe and our partners use information collected through cookies and other identifiers from your device to improve experience on our site, analyse how it is used and to show personalised advertising.\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can opt out of the sale or sharing of your data, at any time clicking the \\\"Do Not Sell or Share my Data\\\" button at the bottom of the webpage.\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please note that your preferences are browser specific.\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3305, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Use of our website and any of our services represents your acceptance of the use ofcookiesand consent to the practices described in ourPrivacy NoticeandTerms and Conditions.\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": []}]}"